express.js is a way for the files to communicate to eachother

POST in HTTP request
GET retrieves the resource from the server
DELETE deletes a specified reseource
PUT replaces a specified ressource with a paylaod

web browser, creates a path from the which ever request was made

REST - REPRESENTATIONAL STANDARD TRANSFER

express.static nany files that are passed as the first parameter. it will give u access to the directory.